* Hatsu-uma Festival (early {{ill|lt=February|Q109|WD=Q109|1=February}})
* Tsushima Shrine {{ill|lt=annual festival|Q11385469|WD=Q11385469|1=Reisai}} ({{ill|lt=July|Q121|WD=Q121|1=July}}, Marine Day)
